SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT A.Ebene1,A.Ebene2,A.Ebene3,A.Ebene4,A.Kunden_Nr,A.ZentralerRechnEmpf FROM AUFTRAGKOPF A WITH(NOLOCK) inner join SRDRUCK_GF_TMP B WITH(NOLOCK) on (a.Ebene1=b.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=b.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=b.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=b.Ebene4 and isnull(a.Geschaeftsfall,'')=b.GF) where A.Ebene1 = :1 AND A.Ebene2 = :2 AND A.Ebene3 = :3 AND A.Ebene4 = :4 AND A.AuftragsNr BETWEEN :5 AND :6 and a.Kunden_Nr BETWEEN :7 AND :11 and b.Aktiviert =1 AND A.Rechnung_drucken=1 AND ohne__Berechnung=0 and Sammelrechnung=1 and an_Lager_buchen=0 and Lieferschein_dr=0 :8 :9 :10 group by a.Ebene1,a.Ebene2,a.Ebene3,a.Ebene4,a.Kunden_Nr,A.ZentralerRechnEmpf

Text.val: Nachbildung des Group Suffix, da sonst Druck zu oft

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT A.Ebene1,A.Ebene2,A.Ebene3,A.Ebene4,A.AuftragsNr,A.Kunden_Nr FROM AUFTRAGKOPF A with(NOLOCK) inner join SRDRUCK_GF_TMP B with(NOLOCK)on (a.Ebene1=b.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=b.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=b.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=b.Ebene4 and (a.Geschaeftsfall=b.GF or (a.Geschaeftsfall is null and b.GF is null))) where A.Ebene1 = :1 AND A.Ebene2 = :2 AND A.Ebene3 = :3 AND A.Ebene4 = :4 AND A.AuftragsNr BETWEEN :5 AND :6 and a.Kunden_Nr BETWEEN :7 AND :11 and b.Aktiviert =1 AND A.Rechnung_drucken=1 AND ohne__Berechnung=0 and Sammelrechnung=1 and an_Lager_buchen=0 and Lieferschein_dr=0:8 :9 :10 order by a.Ebene1,a.Ebene2,a.Ebene3,a.Ebene4,a.Kunden_Nr,a.AuftragsNr
